{
  "texts": [
    "This method helps in determining and reducing WCET, thereby simplifying task scheduling and minimizing the total WCET of all tasks.",
    "The proposed approach integrates a dynamic cache-locking algorithm with a heuristic local optimal task scheduling algorithm.",
    "This integration optimizes task scheduling by making the best use of cache, allowing tasks to meet their deadlines efficiently.",
    "Experiments using benchmarks from the Mälardalen WCET benchmark suite demonstrate the effectiveness of this approach.",
    "The results show that compared to no-cache task scheduling, the approach achieves average improvements of 3.22%, 12.68%, 18.96%, and 19.12% for cache sizes of 256B, 512B, 1KB, and 2KB, respectively."
  ]
}